                <li class="volunteer-li"><strong>Guide Dog Trainer Assistant:</strong> Assist in training and socializing guide dogs under experienced trainers.</li>
                <li class="volunteer-li"><strong>Community Outreach Coordinator:</strong> Organize and execute outreach programs to raise awareness and engage with local communities.</li>
                <li class="volunteer-li"><strong>Administrative Support Volunteer:</strong> Help with day-to-day administrative tasks, ensuring smooth operations.</li>
                <li class="volunteer-li"><strong>Fundraising Event Organizer:</strong> Plan and execute fundraising events, coordinating logistics and mobilizing volunteers.</li>
                <li class="volunteer-li"><strong>Social Media Ambassador:</strong> Manage the organization's social media presence, promoting events, stories, and awareness campaigns.</li>
            </ul>
                
